text = "[Tutorial]
WASD: Move
Mouse: Camera
Arrow: camera offset
Wheel or -,=: zoom_in_out
ESC: free mouse

F11: full screen
-------
F or left click : USE OBJECT
Q: unequip
R: interact /pick things
E: [not yet here] Pick object
T: Drop item
C: Eat

1,2,3,4: equip item
--------------
debug part

M: spawn a sheep
F1: show bin
"

